description:
Danny starts the show off talking about the Golden Gl*be nominations and the Southern Charm/ARod drama. Then, stars of Breaking News In Yuba County (out Feb. 12) Mila Kunis and Juliette Lewis stop by to talk about RHOBH, The Other Sister, a new Bad Mom's movie, and more! Then, Danny dives in to the Real Housewives of Salt Lake City finale, which featured Seth/Meredith banana work, Mary being rude to her congregation and then learning what oxygen is, and Jen owning it. After RHOSLC, Danny talks this week's Real Housewives of Dallas!


Golden Globes/Southern Charm

Mila Kunis/Juliette Lewis Interview: 6:49ish

RHOSLC Recap: 13:45ish

RHOD Recap: 40:12ish
